want run?

best way 
git clone https://github.com/Addisu544/job-board.git
cd job-board
docker compose up -d (this create both backend api and postgresql)
cd client
npm run  dev


1. Pull image
docker pull addisu544/backend-api:latest
2. Run the container

docker run -d \
  --name jobboard-api \
  -p 5000:5000 \
  addisu544/backend-api:latest

cd client
npm run  dev




